#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

long long int hcf(long long int num1, long long int num2)
{
    if (num1<num2)
    {
        long long int temp = num1;
        num1 = num2;
        num2 = temp;
    }
    long long int rem = num1 % num2;
    while (rem!=0)
    {
        num1 = num2;
        num2 = rem;
        rem = num1 % rem;
    }
    return num2;
}

int main()
{
    int t, i, j;
    scanf("\n%i", &t);
    while(t--)
    {
        scanf("\n%i", &i);
        long long int array[i];
        for (j=0; j<i; j++)
            scanf("\n%lli", &array[j]);
        long long int ans;
        ans = hcf(array[0], array[1]);
        for (j=2; j<i; j++)
            ans = hcf(ans, array[j]);
        printf("%lli\n", ans);
    }
    return 0;
}
